// Military faction lair — a vertical platforming tower with the
// General as the faction leader at the top. (The sprite asset id
// stays `absurd_general` because that's the generator archetype;
// the in-game display name is just "General".)
//
// Layout (480 wide × 1280 tall — taller than other labs to feel like a tower):
//
//   +--------------------+  y = 0
//   |  ▒▒▒ ceiling ▒▒▒  |
//   |   trophy ┐        |
//   |  alcove  │ [General NPC]
//   |   ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒│         |
//   |          ▒▒        |  trophy floor
//   | ▒▒                 |  ── floor 4 (kite-shaped)
//   |        ▒▒ ▒▒       |  ── floor 3 (jump-up gap)
//   | ▒▒                 |  ── floor 2
//   |        ▒▒          |  ── floor 1.5 (one-way landing)
//   |  ║                 |  ── ladder column
//   |  ║                 |
//   |  ║   [Ent door]    |
//   |  ║                 |
//   | ▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒▒|  y = 1248 (floor)
//   |  ▒▒▒▒▒ floor ▒▒▒▒  |
//   +--------------------+  y = 1280
//
// Movement contract:
// - Player spawns near the entry door (left-bottom).
// - Climb ladder to floor 2 (left platform).
// - Jump right + up to one-way platform (floor 1.5) -> floor 3 staggered platforms.
// - Jump up to floor 4 (right side), then across to trophy alcove.
// - General is in the trophy alcove with patrol_radius=0 (stationary).
//
// Music: fighters_guild_oath_of_steel — published by the radio cue
// pipeline (`ambition_music_renderer radio publish`). The level's
// `music_track` field is what `RoomMetadata` reads to drive
// `RoomMusicRequest` when the player enters.

